jasima.core.simulation

类 SimComponentBase

  • java.lang.Object
    • jasima.core.simulation.SimComponentBase
  • 所有已实现的接口:
    SimComponent, Notifier<SimComponent,java.lang.Object>, ValueStore, java.lang.Cloneable
    直接已知子类:
    JobSource, SimComponentContainerBase, WorkStation

    public class SimComponentBase
extends java.lang.Object
implements SimComponent
    Potential base class for simulation components implementing the interface SimComponent. Additionally this class introduces a name attribute (that is also used in the toString() method).
    作者:
    Torsten Hildebrandt
